WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.600
Listen, read, repeat.

00:03.600 --> 00:08.280
I have my green card and I want to work.

00:08.280 --> 00:11.160
I will call one company.

00:11.160 --> 00:13.840
It is a small company.

00:13.840 --> 00:16.720
It is not a long way from my home.

00:16.720 --> 00:20.760
I think it is a nice place to work.

00:20.760 --> 00:23.000
I have the phone number.

00:23.000 --> 00:27.160
I will call today and ask about work.

00:27.160 --> 00:30.440
Work is a very important thing to find.

